Name: UCSB
Description: A great university on the beach West of Santa Barbara!

Name: Mt. Tamalpais
Description: A Coastal-Redwood-covered mountain in Marin, my home county.

Name: Glacier Point
Description: Highest point on the Southwest rim of Yosemite Valley, California, with the most stunning view Half Dome and Vernal Falls in the park.

Name: Mt. Silex
Description: A striking mountain deep in Colorado's Weminuche Wilderness, whose jagged shape comes from it upturned layers of hard rock that predate terrestrial life!

Name: Monument Valley
Description: A desert valley dotted with eerily beautiful red sandstone hoodoos and mesas in the Navajo Tribal Park, bridging the Utah-Arizona border.

Name: Joshua Tree NP
Description: A park in the South-central Californian Mojave and Sonora Deserts known for its crumbling granite domes and leafy-trunked Joshua Trees.
